{
  "name": "make-track-labels-part-of-the-20260326-2002",
  "idea": "Make track labels part of the timeline canvas so they're always perfectly aligned with their rows. Currently track labels are in a separate scrolling column that can get out of sync with the canvas rows. The labels should be rendered inside the same scroll container as the timeline content, positioned at the left edge of each row, so they scroll together and stay aligned during drag-to-reorder. The drag handle should move both the label and the row content together as one unit.",
